templateAssets.content: Due to high demand, admission to SDSU is highly competitive. General admission information is available at:http://arweb.sdsu.edu/es/admissions/transfers/index.html
Competency (successfully completing the third college semester or fifth college quarter) is required in one foreign language to fulfill graduation requirements for this major.
Complete with a minimum GPA of 2.20 and a grade of C (2.0) or better: HIST 100, HIST 101, and six lower division units of history electives. These courses cannot be taken for credit/no credit (Cr/NC)
